    "S": "A vibrant Mediterranean-inspired bowl featuring crispy baked falafels made with chickpeas, hemp seeds, and aromatic herbs. Served over fresh greens with cucumber, tomatoes, kalamata olives, feta cheese, and a creamy herbed yogurt sauce. This nutritious, grain-free meal is naturally gluten-free and bursting with Mediterranean flavors."
